\f1\fs26 \cf2 \cb3 How uniform are the rates of spreading along a specific mid-ocean ridge? How consistent are the directions of spreading along each of the six mid-ocean ridges (i.e. N. Atlantic, S. Atlantic, NE Pacific, E Pacific, S Pacific & Red Sea)?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\sa200

\i \cf2 A strong answer will compare the values for rates (mm/yr) and direction (azimuth) of spreading for the two locations for each of the six ridges noting the similarities and/or differences in the values for each individual ridge.
\i0 \
\
